docs/private/
transcripts/
bazel-*
*.gen.go

# Bazel module lock — regenerated; safe to commit but noisy.
MODULE.bazel.lock

# Per-project session store created at runtime (subprocess transcripts,
# AppModel snapshots, worktrees) — see DESIGN.md §4.6.
.gala_team/

# Bazel-managed local workspace cache for transpiled GALA stdlib;
# regenerated on every `bazel build`, never edited by hand.
.gala/
# Local Claude Code agent config — opaque to the project. Project-
# scoped slash-command skills live under .claude/skills and ARE
# tracked (carve-out below).
.claude/*
!.claude/skills/
!.claude/skills/**

# Local team config — references docs in sibling checkouts (e.g.
# ../gala_simple/docs), so the layout assumption shouldn't be baked
# into the public repo. Each maintainer keeps their own.
team.yaml
